      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Add</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Edit not connected and connected VPN</li>\n<li>Connect/Disconnect VPN from Settings page</li>\n<li>Add TLS Certificate on VPN</li>\n<li>Add encryption card on VPN</li>\n<li>\n<span>View interrupted VPN reconnection</span><span></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Include timezone on the filename when downloading logs</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bugs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Some users were unable to login to DXP Cloud via SSO</li>\n<li>Activity/alert was missing for autoscale down event</li>\n</ul>"
